<h1>Confirm Your Email Change</h1>

<p>
  We received a request to change your MOSSLET account email address from your current email to <EmailComponents.highlight color="teal"><strong>{@new_email}</strong></EmailComponents.highlight>.
</p>

<p>
  To complete this change and ensure you continue receiving important account updates, please confirm your new email address by clicking the button below:
</p>

<EmailComponents.button_centered to={@url} color="cyan" size="lg">
  Confirm New Email Address
</EmailComponents.button_centered>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="warning">
  <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours for your security.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>Once confirmed, you'll use <strong>{@new_email}</strong> to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>🔑 Sign in to your MOSSLET account</li>
  <li>📧 Receive account notifications and updates</li>
  <li>🔒 Access password reset and security features</li>
  <li>💬 Continue your private conversations</li>
</ul>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you're having trouble clicking the confirmation button, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
    <a href={@url}>{@url}</a>
  </EmailComponents.small_text>

  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you didn't request this email change, please contact our support team immediately at support@mosslet.com or ignore this email if you believe it was sent in error.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
